        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教学】《MH Wilds 魔物猎人荒野》优化设定集     N 卡用 FSR FG 比 DLSS FG 快</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mh-wilds-tips</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 11:46:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294914</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>这两天见到已有不少人出 Post 讲已打爆了《MH Wilds 魔物猎人荒野》，又话短云云&#8230;&#8230;小编还未有时间真正去体验只 Game，刚试了一些 PC 版的优化小技巧，另外又测试到《MHW》的 FSR + Frame Gen 的效果都不错，除了比 DLSS + Frame Gen 的效能更好，在高速战斗的画面亦不察觉到有什么鬼影，当然要与大家分享一下啦，特别是对于 30 系旧卡的用家来讲，这方面的设定就更加重要了 (30 系或之前旧卡的用家是用不到 DLSS 的 Frame Gen 嘛)。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_07_891" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999853/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999853_9c2b30203c_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_07_891" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">使用 FSR + Frame Gen，在战斗时的性能也相当稳定，也暂时未察觉到有鬼影问题。</p><h2>测试平台</h2><p>Minisforum AtomMan G7 Ti<br /><span class="title">CPU：</span><span class="value">Intel Core i9-14900HX<br /></span><span class="title">Display Card：</span><span class="value">Nvidia GeForce RTX 4070 Laptop 8GB<br /></span><span class="title">Ram：</span><span class="value">32GB DDR5<br /></span>Storage：<span class="value">1TB SSD</span></p><p><a title="IMG_8141" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54356899032/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54356899032_186d5315d1_h.jpg" alt="IMG_8141" width="862" height="1600" /></a></p><p>今次是采用 Minisforum 的 Mini PC 作为测试，内有 <span class="value">RTX 4070 的 Laptop 版，就试试它在 2K 及 4K 画面方面的表现如何。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_14_59_53_425" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999938/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999938_705140148c_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_14_59_53_425" width="1600" height="900" /></a> 画面是用 4K 解像度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_02_43_314" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357779886/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357779886_0fd57394da_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_02_43_314" width="1600" height="900" /></a>设定：解像度为 4K，材质设定为高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_58_26_897" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985069/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985069_8576e6d3df_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_58_26_897" width="1600" height="900" /></a>4K 解像度，设定为 DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，在营地中的速度为 49FPS。<a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_59_05_917" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985059/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985059_455cf016b1_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_59_05_917" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">4K 解像度，设定为 FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，在营地中的速度提升至 62 FPS。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_25_771" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357984999/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357984999_8dd7bd8e1f_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_25_771" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">之后将画面设定为 2K 解像度，在另一岩石背景，DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，材质为高<br /><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_17_026" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357779926/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357779926_00613c9419_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_17_026" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，此场景的速度为 65 FPS</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_53_933" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999878/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999878_f242dc9cfe_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_53_933" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On 的设定</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_30_02_261" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999858/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999858_c2641746bd_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_30_02_261" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，速度升至 93FPS 了</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_03_645" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54358182505/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54358182505_dc3caa17d9_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_03_645" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">设定好 FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，之后在战斗场景中，也有 8X FPS，速度也有很好的表现。</p><p>测试结果：在这部 Mini PC AtomMan G7 Ti 测试中，显卡为 RTX 4070 <span class="value">Laptop 版，设定为 FSR+Frame Gen 的速度表现，的确是比用 DLSS + Frame Gen 的表现来得好，由 65FPS 提升至 93FPS，实试提升效能最高达到 43%，而画面方面亦察觉不到有什么特别不同之处；而在战斗及高速动作时，用上 FSR 后又未有察觉到鬼影的问题。</span></p><h2>其他提升速度小技巧</h2><p>《MHW》的画质设定非常仔细，有很多细项可以微调，一些无关痛痒的画面细节项目，调整好后也有助提升游戏的 FPS，现在说几个不太影响到画质而又难以察觉的项目。可以将设定为低至中，都会有少量 FPS 的提升。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_59_40_385" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359925644/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359925644_9b255b3fb6_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_59_40_385" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">未修改设定之前，FPS 为 86</p><p>一些设定调整如下：</p><p>体积雾：低<br />
云品质：中<br />
毛皮品质：低</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_58_811" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359722366/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359722366_ae18b30899_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_58_811" width="1600" height="900" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_22_996" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359722371/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359722371_a27ceebe62_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_22_996" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_00_520" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359949278/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359949278_093ebc8199_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_00_520" width="1600" height="900" /></a> 设定调整后 FPS 都会有一些增长，今次增长至 91，有 6% 左右的增长，都不错呀</p><p>今次的示范已有 6% 左右的 FPS 提升，其他的设定大家都可以试试，若果不太在意的画面背景项目调整也可以设定为低或关闭，都会有助 FPS 的提升。</p><h2>免费 DLC 高解析度材质不要碰</h2><p>如果你是用 30 系或之前的旧卡，或者是 4080 或以下的 40 系卡，又或者是 VRAM 低于 12GB 的显卡，还是不要碰高解析度材质了，这个是免费的 DLC，不下载又可以悭 75GB 空间，而且用上后速度会超慢的，画面又不是有很明显的分别&#8230;&#8230;当然如果你是用旗舰级的高阶显示卡 + 4K 解像 + 大 Mon 玩就另作别论。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_00_50_332" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985044/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985044_2d90d4b2e6_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_00_50_332" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><h2>后记：PC 版另一乐趣就是 Mod</h2><p>如果玩开 PC 版的玩家，都知道其中一样乐趣就是装 Mod 了，现时短短三天 MH Wilds 都已有数十个 Mod 推出了，即刻拣几个来玩玩先。迟些有机会再与大家分享一下有趣及实用的 Mod。</p><p><a title="20250302201631_1" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54360372790/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54360372790_5f23a6a16f_h.jpg" alt="20250302201631_1" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p><a title="20250302190210_1" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54360111609/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54360111609_17eb2ddbcf_h.jpg" alt="20250302190210_1" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/">【教学】《MH Wilds 魔物猎人荒野》优化设定集     N 卡用 FSR FG 比 DLSS FG 快</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
