        <item>
            <title>Lenovo AI Now 本地 AI 平台登场，离线私隐兼备，全面进攻智能笔电市场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-ai-now</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
