            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294942</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Lenovo 在香港及海外多个市场同步发布最新人工智能技术平台 Lenovo AI Now，这套专为笔电用家打造的 AI 工具，重点强调离线运作、高度个人化以及数据私隐保护三大优势。Lenovo AI Now 会陆续搭载在 IdeaPad、Yoga、Legion 以及 LOQ 等不同系列笔电上，让更多用家享受高效便捷的 AI 辅助体验。这次发布亦同时展示多款内建 AI 功能的新硬件，全面展示 Lenovo 进攻 AI 应用市场的最新布局。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo 在香港举行的产品展示会上，除展示即将于本地市场推出的新款笔电与游戏掌机，最吸引目光的焦点，无疑是 AI 平台 Lenovo AI Now。这个全新 AI 平台采用本地大型语言模型（LLM），核心技术源自 Meta Llama 3，无需依赖云端运算，就可直接在用家装置内完成文件搜寻、总结、生成等操作，私隐保障方面远胜传统云端 AI 助手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo AI Now 内置知识助手（Knowledge Assistant），用家可将 Word、Excel、PowerPoint、PDF 等档案加入个人知识库，然后透过自然语言对话形式，快速提取关键资讯，甚至可即时生成报告摘要或工作整理，特别适合需要处理大量文件的学生及专业人士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis-694x547.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="547" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis-694x547.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis.jpeg 1142w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo 同时展示另一套针对创意工作者的 AI 工具 Lenovo Creator Zone，这个平台采用优化版 Stable Diffusion 3.0，支援文字描述生成图片，亦可透过草图或参考图片快速生成视觉素材。平台还加入背景替换、图层合并、颜色调整等功能，令图像编辑工作变得更简单。</p><p>针对学习市场，Lenovo 推出 Lenovo Learning Zone，这套 AI 学习平台可以录制课堂语音，并即时转换为文字摘要，还可自动生成小测验，协助用家巩固学习重点。平台亦支援将 YouTube 教学影片或新闻影片转换为笔记，提升自学效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294947" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在海外发布会上，Lenovo 亦同步展示未来 AI 产品概念，包括全新 AI Buddy 视觉互动助手，这个 AI Buddy 不单可分析用家情绪，还可根据需求提供行程提醒、待办事项提示等功能，形象接近个人化虚拟管家。另一个概念产品 Home AI Brain，则针对家庭应用，能自动将家庭活动影片剪辑成回顾影片，并支援跨装置共享与编辑，提升全家数码回忆整理体验。</p><h2 data-start="385" data-end="572">Lenovo 各种支援 AI 产品</h2><p data-start="574" data-end="624"><strong data-start="574" data-end="622">Yoga 9 2-in-1 Aura Edition AI 算力爆棚，二合一设计灵活百变</strong></p><p data-start="626" data-end="831">Yoga 9 2-in-1 Aura Edition 支援 Copilot+ 功能的二合一笔电内置 Intel Core Ultra 7 处理器与 Intel Arc 显示核心，能够轻松应对各类智能助手、AI 图像生成与实时翻译等功能。二合一设计让装置能在笔电与平板模式之间灵活切换，特别适合需要多场景工作或学习的用家。</p><p data-start="626" data-end="831"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294950" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="833" data-end="874"><strong data-start="833" data-end="872">Idea Tab Pro 大屏娱乐平板，内建 Google AI 功能</strong></p><p data-start="876" data-end="1084">Idea Tab Pro 新一代高性能平板电脑，配备 12.7 吋 3K 解像度屏幕，整合 Google AI，支援 Circle to Search 图像搜寻功能与 AI 即时翻译，为影音娱乐与学习带来更多智能化便利</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga 7i 2-in-1</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294951" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga Slim 7i Aura Edition</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294952" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga Slim 9i</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/">Lenovo AI Now 本地 AI 平台登场，离线私隐兼备，全面进攻智能笔电市场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
